Name: How can I register for this event?
Description: By registering via the eventbrite link we provided here: https://www.eventbrite.com.au/e/careerfest-2022-tickets-362937304247

Name: How does the event work?
Description:
Career Fest consists of two main events:

  • Webinar

            Students will have the opportunity to hear from and ask questions to industry professionals. 

  • Networking & Information Session

            Students will get to speak one-on-one with the desired companies/recruiters.

            In this event, students will also get more information about job openings from each company.

                  - For more detail on the event schedule, please refer to our website.

Name: Is this a free event?
Description: Yes, this event is created entirely for free.

Name: What if I have to cancel my career attendant experience?
Description:
By applying to the career fest PPIA 2022, you have an opportunity and experience to meet the employer directly.  Participants use at least a week in advance; you should be able to follow through on this commitment.

Suppose a student participant cannot follow through on their commitment to attending the career fest experience for any reason. In that case, the student participant MUST notify the career fest admin within two business days of the career fest experience, except in the case of extenuating circumstances (such as natural disasters).
